&lt;p&gt;&lt;em&gt;Displayed pay range (base salary) is a guide and local market specific. The pay offered to a successful candidate will be based on skill set and professional experience assessed throughout the interview process.&lt;/em&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;em&gt;EUR 42,150 - EUR 63,000&lt;/em&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
