&lt;p class=&quot;PDq2pG_selectionAnchorContainer&quot; data-start=&quot;0&quot; data-end=&quot;118&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-family: helvetica, arial, sans-serif;&quot;&gt;&lt;strong data-start=&quot;0&quot; data-end=&quot;78&quot;&gt;Expression of Interest: Territory Field Sales – Professional Haircare (UK)&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;br data-start=&quot;78&quot; data-end=&quot;81&quot;&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;hover:entity-accent entity-underline inline cursor-pointer align-baseline&quot; style=&quot;font-family: helvetica, arial, sans-serif;&quot;&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;whitespace-normal&quot;&gt;Kao&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p data-start=&quot;120&quot; data-end=&quot;400&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-family: helvetica, arial, sans-serif;&quot;&gt;Are you passionate about professional haircare, relationship-led sales, and building trusted partnerships with salons and stylists? We are inviting &lt;strong data-start=&quot;268&quot; data-end=&quot;303&quot;&gt;general expressions of interest&lt;/strong&gt; for future Territory Field Sales opportunities within the Professional Haircare division at Kao.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p data-start=&quot;402&quot; data-end=&quot;627&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-family: helvetica, arial, sans-serif;&quot;&gt;While there may not be an immediate vacancy, we are building a talent pipeline so that when roles open, we can quickly connect with individuals who already understand (or are excited to enter) the professional salon industry.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;h3 data-section-id=&quot;1u5gnl7&quot; data-start=&quot;634&quot; data-end=&quot;659&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-family: helvetica, arial, sans-serif;&quot;&gt;About the Opportunity&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/h3&gt;
&lt;p data-start=&quot;660&quot; data-end=&quot;951&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-family: helvetica, arial, sans-serif;&quot;&gt;As a Territory Field Sales professional in the Professional Haircare sector, you would represent Kao’s salon portfolio across your territory, supporting salon growth, education, and brand success. You would act as both a commercial partner and a trusted advisor to salon owners and stylists.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p data-start=&quot;953&quot; data-end=&quot;981&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-family: helvetica, arial, sans-serif;&quot;&gt;Typical focus areas include:&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;ul data-start=&quot;982&quot; data-end=&quot;1366&quot;&gt;
&lt;li style=&quot;font-family: helvetica, arial, sans-serif;&quot; data-section-id=&quot;7e6f93&quot; data-start=&quot;982&quot; data-end=&quot;1049&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-family: helvetica, arial, sans-serif;&quot;&gt;Developing long-term relationships with salons and key accounts&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li style=&quot;font-family: helvetica, arial, sans-serif;&quot; data-section-id=&quot;1audxzn&quot; data-start=&quot;1050&quot; data-end=&quot;1132&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-family: helvetica, arial, sans-serif;&quot;&gt;Driving territory growth through new business and existing account development&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li style=&quot;font-family: helvetica, arial, sans-serif;&quot; data-section-id=&quot;3zzlq7&quot; data-start=&quot;1198&quot; data-end=&quot;1284&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-family: helvetica, arial, sans-serif;&quot;&gt;Collaborating with education and marketing teams to support launches and campaigns&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li style=&quot;font-family: helvetica, arial, sans-serif;&quot; data-section-id=&quot;pjha4j&quot; data-start=&quot;1285&quot; data-end=&quot;1366&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-family: helvetica, arial, sans-serif;&quot;&gt;Identifying local market opportunities and translating them into sales growth&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
&lt;h3 data-section-id=&quot;ebiqzw&quot; data-start=&quot;1373&quot; data-end=&quot;1399&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-family: helvetica, arial, sans-serif;

&lt;p&gt;Kao Professional Hair is home to a portfolio of iconic professional salon brands, including Goldwell, KERASILK, KMS Hair, Oribe, and VARIS. Our mission is simple: to enrich the lives of stylists, salon owners, and their clients. Through innovation, education, and partnership, we&#39;re dedicated to making life more beautiful.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;About the Role: &lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Colour-Focused Salon Educator – covering Northern England, ideally located in Sheffield, Manchester or Leeds area.&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;This is a varied and rewarding role for someone who loves being on the move. You&#39;ll travel across your region, working to a structured journey plan, engaging directly with salons and building meaningful, long-term relationships. The role includes regular travel, with some overnight stays required depending on location and business needs.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;As a trusted expert and brand representative, you&#39;ll play a key role in developing hairdressers&#39; technical skills -particularly in colour - helping them deliver exceptional results using Goldwell products. You&#39;ll also collaborate closely with the sales team to grow the business, identifying new opportunities and supporting salons in transitioning to Goldwell.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;This role is ideal for someone who enjoys a mix of hands-on education, commercial awareness, and relationship management.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Key Responsibilities:&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Deliver engaging, high-quality training to salon teams, supporting both new and existing accounts in your region&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Partner with the sales team to align on customer needs and drive best practice across salons&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Showcase new products, promotions, and education initiatives at meetings and events&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Plan and manage your territory effectively to maximise impact and coverage&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Continuously develop your own skills through ongoing training and industry insights&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Represent Kao as a passionate Brand Ambassador at industry and company events&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Maintain accurate reporting and administrative records&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;What We&#39;re Looking For:&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Minimum of 8 years&#39; experience within the professional hairdressing industry.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Proven experience delivering hair education is required&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Prior expertise across all aspects of hairdressing, including cutting, colouring, styling, and retail within a salon environment.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Experience in presenting and basic management, with the ability to support, guide, and influence salon teams.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Knowledge of commercial salon operations, including the pressures of long working days, varied salon cultures, and the ability to prioritise workload effectively.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Ability to adapt communication and training styles to suit different personalities and team dynamics within salon environments.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Commercial awareness with an understanding of how education can support business growth and product distribution.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Basic working knowledge of Microsoft Office programs (such as Outlook, PowerPoint, and Excel).&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;What We Offer&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Company car and company card.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Flexible working and competitive compensation packages.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Pension and insurance plans.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;You will enjoy 25 days holiday, plus your birthday off, with the option to buy up to 5 extra days (pro-rata).&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Hiring Process&lt;/strong&gt; Kao values diversity and individuality, believing equal opportunity and inclusion make us stronger. We welcome app

&lt;p&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif;&quot;&gt;&lt;strong&gt;The role:&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif;&quot;&gt;This is a strategic role that requires passion &amp;amp; excitement for continuous improvement in both areas of Health, Safety and Environmental Engineering (HSE). Reporting to the Sr Facilities Manager the HSE Engineer for the Americas region will be responsible for developing, facilitating, training &amp;amp; implementing HSE programs and policies.&amp;nbsp;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif;&quot;&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif;&quot;&gt;You&amp;nbsp; will be required to spend time in all areas of the Plant &amp;amp; Warehouse to provide a continually evolving Health -Safety strategy while ensuring management and employees understand the programs and how to implement. Maintain a working knowledge of agency requirements and maintain federal, state and local relationships with appropriate regulatory agencies. Develop &amp;amp; maintain a high level of professional competence in the health- Safety field.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif;&quot;&gt;&lt;strong&gt;At Kao, we offer an amazing benefits that are available to you on your first day of employment (healthcare, 401(k) plus company match, etc.), 32 total days off (vacation + holidays + sick) and a reasonable salary range of $80,000 - $105,000.&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif;&quot;&gt;&lt;strong&gt;What you will do:&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li style=&quot;font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif;&quot;&gt;Ensure completion and accuracy of all required documentation and submittal for governing agencies including but not limited to Federal, State, and local Environmental compliance&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/li&gt;
